{"tid":182081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前我讀小學，功課同考試都難過而家好多","createTime":"2017-04-01T05:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T11:28:11.000Z","uid":49769,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96ced8f246907aa63c6f0d011db7b6238d048aa9","tid":182081,"uid":49769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"而家又話怕TSA又怕多功課乜乜乜<br />\n我而以平均一日都差唔多8-10份功課，最多試過17份，末一樣咁做<br />\n我以前仲要隔日默書or quiz<br />\n以前dictation or quiz拿9成or full mark係正常，唔會特別高興<br />\n重點係我都仲有好多時間玩同hea<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話針對，而家新一代小學生，大部分都係蝗<br />\n蝗家長唔識教，班蝗又好撚蠢又懶(多次同蝗補習)<br />\n我唔係話教育制度冇問題，<br />\n只係想講而家小學問題比人誇大左<br />\n<br />\n有冇人認同?<br />\n<br />\n利申, 90後 and 有多次同蝗小學生補習"},{"pid":"c3052806fd37f92ff3714e9232b78685d4a5eff5","tid":182081,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"以前你全日制定上下午校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac723e0e002b7ec9730dec3e05942ef4606cf2b1","tid":182081,"uid":49769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前你全日制定上下午校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原本上下午，最後2年轉左全日"},{"pid":"c9ac587a975d83d9ecea7ed4f09124906841af32","tid":182081,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"上午校 十幾樣功課係基本 上堂偷做一半 返歸做一半 四點補完習就落街踢波飛單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9733f6a6dc7febb8477b107342b89cc3fd326f60","tid":182081,"uid":51649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"支那種真係特別蠢"},{"pid":"93fb1f2d5ac44dc618547a1206063055750ff57c","tid":182081,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"依家d家長有問題，就算唔俾咁多功課你個仔，你咪又係幫佢報一大堆興趣班呀補習班呀，買一大籮補充練習俾佢做，一樣係無得抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59176779